Package: nymea-plugin-zwave-generic
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: nymea integration plugin for Z-Wave Spec compliant devices
 This package contains the nymea integration plugin for Z-Wave devices which
 adhere to the specification and thus can be handled in a unified and generic manner.


Package: nymea-plugin-zwave-fibaro
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: nymea integration plugin for Fibaro Z-Wave devices
 This package contains the nymea integration plugin for Z-Wave based devices
 made by Fibaro.


Package: nymea-plugin-zwave-qubino
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: nymea integration plugin for Qubino Z-Wave devices
 This package contains the nymea integration plugin for Z-Wave based devices
 made by Qubino.


Package: nymea-plugin-zwave-springswindowfashions
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: nymea integration plugin for Springs Window Fashions Z-Wave devices
 This package contains the nymea integration plugin for Z-Wave based devices
 made by Springs Window Fashions.


Package: nymea-plugins-zwave
Section: libs    
Architecture: all
Depends: nymea-plugin-zwave-fibaro,
         nymea-plugin-zwave-generic,
         nymea-plugin-zwave-qubino,
         nymea-plugin-zwave-springswindowfashions,
Description: Z-Wave integration plugins for nymea - meta package
 This package will install all Z-Wave related integration plugins for nymea.
